Ngou5 Kok-seng5 e5 heng5-hong2 bo5 kong2 kai3-ho2, sin-the2 chin hi-lam2, chiunn7 hoe2-chhia chin3-cheng5, A-tek ti7 chhia-thau5 e5 chhan-thiann be2 chit8-oann2 sio-thng hou7 lim--loeh, i chiah u7 tam7-poh8-a2 khui3-lat8.
“Siau3-lian5--e5, si7 Juan kio3 li2 lai5--e5 tioh8--bo5.” Ngou5 Kok-seng5 kong2-oe7 chin se3-siann, A-tek ai3 ka7 hi7-a2 oa2 ti7 i e5 chhui3 chiah thiann e7 tioh8, “Goa2 kiong2-kiann bo5 hoat-tou7 kap li2 che7 hoe2-chhia khi3-kau3 hit-e5 Shangri-la--ah, kin-a2-jit8 tu2-ho2 si7 goa2 kau2-chap8 hoe3 e5 senn-jit8, na7 chit-jit8 lai5 soah-kou2 kam2 m7-si7 chin hah8-gi5--leh.” A-tek ti7 Espana chiah ku2--ah, te7-it-kai2 thiann lang5 teh kong2 Tai5-oan5-oe7.
“Ngou5 phok-su7, li2 e7 ho2--khi2-lai5 lah, li2 tui3 jin5-lui7 e5 pang-chan7 chiah-nih8 toa7, thinn-kong peh e7 po2-pi3--li2.”
“Pang-chan7?” Ngou5 Kok-seng5 chin chiah8-lat8 teh chhio3, “Siau3-lain5--e5, li2 liah8-cho3 to7-tek chiann5-si7 thai3-chou2-pai5?”
A-tek m7-chai beh an2-choann2 ka7 in3.
“Siong7-kai3 sun5-sui2 e5 to7-tek si7 bo5 jin7-ho5 peh8-chhat8--e5, siau3-lian5--e5, li2 kam2 e7 in-ui7 bo5-ai3 kong2 peh8-chhat8 lai5 hoan2-poe7 ka-ti7 e5 kok-ka.”
“U7 e5 tai7-chi3 pun2-te2 to7-si7 ai3 chai khin-tang7, ai3 chai sio cheng2-hoe7--ah...” A-tek in3 kah hi-sim hi-sim.
“Na7 an2-ne, li2 chun2-pi7 beh the3 kah sim2-mih8 kham2-cham7? Koh lai5, siann2-lang5 u7 chu-keh lai5 koat-teng7 chit8-e5 phiau-chun2, ti7 bou2-mih8-khoan2 tai7-chi3 bou2-mih8-khoan2 si5-kan, lan2 to7 e7-tang3 ka7 to7-tek e5 goan5-chek ka7 hiat-kak, m7-koh ti7 bou2-mih8-khoan2 tai7-chi3 bou2-mih8-khoan2 si5-kan to7 be7-eng7-tit--leh? To7-tek u7 si5-chun7 to7 chhin-chhiunn7 si7 li7-ek e5 hun-phenn, khoann3 li2 si7 beh tui3-tiong7 ti7 kou3 bou2 chit8-e5 lang5, bou2 chit8-tin7 lang5, iah8-si7 chit se3-kan sou2-u7 e5 lang5, koh lai5, si5-kan--leh, li2 beh khoann3 joa7 ku2-tng5? Kok-ka e5 khi2-loh8 ti7 jin5-lui7 lek8-su2 lai5 khoann3, u7-iann2 si7 chin te2, lan2 hong3-kiam jin7-ui7 in-ui7 ai3-kok lai5 hi-seng to7-tek e5 goan5-chek kam2 m7-si7?”
A-tek choann-a2 pinn2-chhui3, i seng5-jin7 i bo5 siunn7 chiah che7.
“Gun2 u7-iann2 s7 kian7-tiu koh hoat chhui3-chhiu,” Ngou5 Kok-seng5 tun3-tenn--chit8-e5, “chit kui2-tang goa2 u7 teh siunn7 nng7-hang7 tai7-chi3, chit8-hang7 si7 in hit-khaon2 cho3-hoat e7 khi3 tit-sit tioh8 joa7-che7 lang5, koh e7 khi3 pai7-hai7 joa7-che7 lang5 hian7-sit8 e5 li7-ek, chit8-e5 oan5-choan5 bo5 chu7-li7 e5 sia7-hoe7 kam2 m7-si7 chu7-ngou2 hoe2-biat8--e5? Chu7-li7-sim na7 bo5--khi3, keng-che3, siong-giap8 kap chu-pun2 chhi7-tiunn5 to7 e7 biat8-bo5, boe2--a7, lan2 kan-tann si7 tng2-khi3 kau3 tau2-oann7 e5 si5-tai7 nia7-tiann7, sui-jian5 u7-lang5 e7 kong2 siong-giap8 kap ki-sut8 e5 chin3-pou7 tui3 jin5-lui7 bo5 it-teng7 si7 ho2 tai7-chi3, m7-koh beh chau5-biat8 siong-giap8 kap chu-pun2 li7-ek, choat8-tui3 u7-lang5 e7 peh khi2-lai5 kap li2 piann3-mia7.” Ngou5 Kok-seng5 kong2 kah chia, pok8-pheng5 sau3 kah chin li7-hai7, A-tek na2 ka7 tah kha-chiah-phiann, na2 kio3 i mai3 koh kong2--ah.
“Che si7 goa2 koe3-khui3 chin3-cheng5 siong7-boe2 e5 kui2-ku3-oe7--ah.” Ngou5 Kok-seng5 an2-ne ka7 in3.
“Te7-ji7-hang7 si7, goa2 u7 tiang-chun7 e7 siunn7-kong2, bo5 tek-khak ‘bo5 to7-tek’ kheng5-sit8 si7 jin5-lui7 kiu5 seng-chun5 kap po2-hou7 ka-ti7 e5 kun-te2, lan2 theh8 peh8-chhat8-oe7 lai5 kong2, tioh8 si2-cheng3 e5 lang5 tui3 ka-ti7 kong2 ‘goa2 it-teng7 e7 ho2--khi2-lai5’, li2 kong2 che si7 ‘peh8-chhat8’ iah8 si7 ‘sin3-sim’--leh? U7 si5-chun7 peh8-chhat8 soah chhin-chhiunn7 si7 teh po2-hou7 lang5 ka-ti7 e5 chit8-khaon2 chhiu2-lou7. Kong2--khi2-lai5, lan2 e5 sin-the2 tui3 lan2 siong7 lau2-sit8, phoa3-penn7 tioh8-siong to7 hou7 li2 thiann3 kah beh si2, li2 kam2 beh ku3-chai7 i thiann3? Kam2 long2 bo5-ai3 chiah8 chi2-thiann3 ioh8-a2? Lau2-sit8 thau3-te2 e5 kiat-ko2, kam2 e7 lian5 ka7 penn7 i hou7 ho2 e5 ki-hoe7 to7 bo5, soah bok8-beng5 ki5-biau7 in-ui7 lau2-sit8 lai5 si2.”
Ngou5 Kok-seng5 kong2 kah siong7-boe2 nng7-sann ku3-oe7 e5 si5, bak8-chiu i2-keng khoeh--loh8, A-tek tan2 chit8-khun3, m7-koh i long2 bo5 koh chhut-siann, chim-chiok ka7 khoann3, lang5 i2-keng koe3-ong2--ah.
A-tek tng2-lai5 kau3 Puigcerda Nuevo i2-keng si7 sann-kenn me5-poann3, lian5-soa3 kui2-a7-kang ou-im, keh-tng2-kang chai2-khi2 chhut-jit8, thinn-khi3 siat-thai2 hoan2-joah8, A-tek kui2-a7-kang an2-ne chhia-poah8-peng2, thiam2 kah it-tit8 khun3 kah e7-pou iau2 peh be7 khi2--lai5, bo5 gi7-gou7 chit8-tin7 lang5 soah ti7 chit-e5 e7-pou lai5 beh ka7 Puigcerda Nuevo hui2 chiann5 penn5-pou, A-tek be7-hu3 kiu3 Milagros, i chau2 to3 chhut--lai5 e5 si5 koh khai-si2 teh pian3-thinn, boe2--a2 poah8 loeh soann-khenn.
Hit-am3 chong2-li2 ti7 tian7-si7 teng2 hoat-piau2 kong2-oe7, kong2: “To7-tek e5 tui-jip si7 chit8-kiann7 chin ho2 e5 tai7-chi3, m7-koh to7-tek e5 bok8-tek si7 beh hou7 kok-ka kap jin5-lui7 koh-khah heng7-hok e5 seng-oah8, to7-tek e5 pun2-sin bo5 eng3-kai chhiann5-cho3 kou-hang7 e5 bok8-tek.”
“Choe3-kin7 lan2-kok tang-pak-pou7 soann-khu hoat-hian7 chit8-e5 in-bou5 chou-chit, chit-e5 chou-chit e5 lang5 chin3-jip8 kau3 lan2 che7-che7 tiong7-iau3 ki-ko3 lai7-te2, pi2-lun7 kong2 Hugo Ferro ham7 Gabino Lara e5 an3-kiann7 long2 kap in u7 koan-he7, tui3 kok-ka sia7-hoe7 u7 chin toa7 e5 pai7-hai7, cheng3-hu2 i2-keng kin2-chiap8 chhu2-li2, tek8-chiong2 pou7-tui7 ti7 soann-khu phah-si2 435 e5 phainn2-tou5, leng7-goa7 u7 chit8-koa2 chau2-thoat--e5, cheng3-hu2 u7 sin3-sim e7 chin-kin2 ka7 in chong2 sa--khi2-lai5, chhiann2 tak8-e5 hong3-sim.”
“In be7 kong2 peh8-chhat8, chin ho2-chang.” Chong2-li2 kong2-soah beh chau2 e5 si5, keng2-chhat chong2-tiunn2 ti7 i e5 hi7-khang pinn an2-ne kong2.
Tann A-tek ti7 hui-leng5 ki-tiunn5 beh chiunn7 hui-leng5-ki--ah, i kui-e5 thau5-khak lai7 ju5-chhang2-chhang2, am3-si5 in-ui7 chiah-e5 tai7-chi3 teh bin5-bang7, jit8--si5 ma7 bo5 hoat-tou7 chau2-siam2 chiah-e5 ju5-su3-bang7.
Chiunn7-ki e5 si5-kan kau3--ah, A-tek pai5-tui7 tan2 beh jip8-khi3 chiunn7-ki-mng5 e5 si5, bo5-i3-tiong soah khoann3-tioh8 pai5 ti7 thau5-cheng5 te7-sann-e5 lang5, chit8-e5 hou5-chhiu--e5, i e5 am-a2-kun2 au7-piah u7 po5-che2 cho3 ki3-ho7, be7-su chit8-chiah boe2-iah8-a2 hioh ti7 hia.
(Tai5-bun5 Bong2-po3 te7 100~102 ki5, 2005 ni5 1~3 goeh8)
